- start as ssh proxy (autoselect port, generate key, set IP address)
- resend packet if unconfirmed too long (~0.2 s, optional or adjustable)
- confirm each N (~10) packets or after ~0.1 s
- packet reordering
- sparse data, autorecovery lost packets
- send as batches (packet includes previous data, MSGTYPE_MDATA)
- crypt magic, generate nonce, check nonce
- if IP changed, perform extra authentication using key2
- extra command-line options (mtu, cmd, window)
- ipv6
- msquic
